OL,3,CNato allies upset US by 'going into
OL,4,Chiding' during Iran war ` Marco Rubio
OL,6,FThe White House is "very upset" with
OL,7,FNato members for "going into hiding"
OL,8,Fduring the Iran war, US secretary of
OL,9,Fstate Marco Rubio has said.
OL,11,FAmerica's top diplomat levelled his
OL,12,Flatest criticism as he headed to a
OL,13,Fmeeting of counterparts from the
OL,14,Fmilitary alliance in Sweden.
OL,16,FAhead of the summit, Mr Rubio also
OL,17,Fspoke to UK Foreign Secretary Yvette
OL,18,FCooper, who is among those expected to
OL,19,Fattend.
OL,26,@nD@TOUnD@_O]oD@ROUoD@dO]
