OL,3,CNato allies upset US by 'going into
OL,4,Chiding' during Iran war ` Marco Rubio
OL,6,FThe discussion included "the
OL,7,Fimportance of Europe providing more of
OL,8,Fits own security and the need for
OL,9,Fincreased defence investment and
OL,10,Fgreater burden sharing in the Nato
OL,11,Falliance", according to the US State
OL,12,FDepartment.
OL,14,FDonald Trump has been scathing over
OL,15,FBritain's reluctance to be drawn into
OL,16,Fthe Iran conflict, accusing Sir Keir
OL,17,FStarmer of being weak and deriding the
OL,18,FRoyal Navy.
OL,26,@nD@YOUsD@IO]
