OL,3,CNato allies upset US by 'going into
OL,4,Chiding' during Iran war ` Marco Rubio
OL,6,FIt sparked reports the US could review
OL,7,Fits position on Britain's claim to the
OL,8,FFalkland Islands as punishment.
OL,10,FThe Prime Minister refused to give the
OL,11,FUS free rein in its use of British
OL,12,Fmilitary bases to carry out attacks
OL,13,Fagainst Iran, with permission limited
OL,14,Fto defensive strikes on missile sites.
OL,16,FThere have also been tensions over the
OL,17,Fresponse of the UK and other countries
OL,18,Fto the crisis in the Strait of Hormuz,
OL,19,Fwhich was open to shipping prior to
OL,20,Fthe US and Israel offensive against
OL,21,FIran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
