OL,3,CNato allies upset US by 'going into
OL,4,Chiding' during Iran war ` Marco Rubio
OL,6,FTehran's stranglehold on the Gulf
OL,7,Fwaterway has shocked economies around
OL,8,Fthe world, including the UK's, and
OL,9,Fseen a spike in oil prices.
OL,11,FWashington has argued Europe needs the
OL,12,Fsea route "much more than we do" and
OL,13,Fensuring free transit of vessels was
OL,14,F"much more their fight than ours".
OL,16,FPlans being overseen by Britain and
OL,17,FFrance to protect shipping in the
OL,18,Fcritical waterway once hostilities end
OL,19,Fhave also been challenged by the US,
OL,20,Fwith Mr Rubio himself arguing "it
OL,21,Fdoesn't make sense".
OL,26,@tD@KOUtD@`O]vD@AOUvD@aO]|D@_OU}D@SO]
