OL,3,CNato allies upset US by 'going into
OL,4,Chiding' during Iran war ` Marco Rubio
OL,6,FSpeaking to reporters in Florida
OL,7,Fbefore flying to the Nato summit, Mr
OL,8,FRubio would not be drawn over reported
OL,9,Fplans by the US to reduce its force
OL,10,Fcontribution to the alliance,
OL,11,Finsisting it was a matter for the
OL,12,Fpresident and defence department.
OL,14,FBut he said: "I don't think anyone is
OL,15,Fshocked to know that the United
OL,16,FStates, and the president in
OL,17,Fparticular, is very disappointed at
OL,18,FNato right now."
OL,26,@vD@NOUzD@PO]
