OL,3,CNato allies upset US by 'going into
OL,4,Chiding' during Iran war ` Marco Rubio
OL,6,FWhile a long-time supporter of the
OL,7,Falliance, Mr Rubio said the refusal by
OL,8,Fmembers, such as Spain, the use of
OL,9,Ftheir bases, made the US question the
OL,10,Fbenefit of membership.
OL,12,FHe added: "Understand that there are
OL,13,Fmany countries in Nato that agree with
OL,14,Fus that Iran can't have a nuclear
OL,15,Fweapon, that Iran is a threat to the
OL,16,Fworld.
OL,18,F"So the president said, 'fine, I'm
OL,19,Fgoing to do something about it'.
OL,26,@tD@KOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
