OL,3,CNato allies upset US by 'going into
OL,4,Chiding' during Iran war ` Marco Rubio
OL,6,F"He's not asking them to commit
OL,7,Ftroops. He's not asking them to send
OL,8,Ftheir fighter jets in. But they refuse
OL,9,Fto do anything.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
