OL,3,CNato allies upset US by 'going into
OL,4,Chiding' during Iran war ` Marco Rubio
OL,6,F"So, I think the president looks at
OL,7,Fthat and says, hold on a second, if
OL,8,Fall these countries around the world
OL,9,Fagree with us that Iran can't have a
OL,10,Fnuclear weapon and this regime is a
OL,11,Fthreat to world peace and security,
OL,12,Fthat already have missiles that can
OL,13,Freach Europe ` they don't have
OL,14,Fmissiles that could reach America yet,
OL,15,Fbut they have missiles that could
OL,16,Freach Europe ` we're actually stepping
OL,17,Fforward to do something about it, and
OL,18,Feveryone goes into hiding.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
