OL,3,CNato allies upset US by 'going into
OL,4,Chiding' during Iran war ` Marco Rubio
OL,6,F"Yeah, I think we were very upset
OL,7,Fabout that. The president has made
OL,8,Fthat very clear."
OL,10,FMr Rubio also lambasted moves by
OL,11,FTehran to impose a levy on ships
OL,12,Fpassing through the Strait of Hormuz.
OL,14,FHe said: "No one in the world is in
OL,15,Ffavour of a tolling system. It can't
OL,16,Fhappen. It would be unacceptable.
OL,18,F"It would make a diplomatic deal
OL,19,Funfeasible if they were to continue to
OL,20,Fpursue that.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@QO]vD@JOUzD@AOU
