OL,3,CNato allies upset US by 'going into
OL,4,Chiding' during Iran war ` Marco Rubio
OL,6,F"So, it's a threat to the world that
OL,7,Fthey would try to do that. And it's
OL,8,Fcompletely illegal, by the way."
OL,10,FMeanwhile, Mr Trump said: "We want it
OL,11,Fopen, we want it free. We don't want
OL,12,Ftolls. It's an international waterway."
OL,14,FIn a statement issued late on
OL,15,FThursday, US State Department
OL,16,Fspokesman Tommy Pigott said:
OL,17,F"Secretary of state Marco Rubio spoke
OL,18,Ftoday with UK Foreign Secretary Yvette
OL,19,FCooper to discuss Iran and ongoing
OL,20,Fefforts to restore freedom of
OL,21,Fnavigation in the Strait of Hormuz.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@`O]rD@[OUtD@gO]yD@AOU
